(3, 39, 'FAQ', 'faq', '<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr">Many people have contacted me regarding on<strong> setting up a web site, mobile app/site or a software solution</strong>. I’ve had the intention to provide them all with a customized solution that fulfills their needs. </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr">Implement a brand new website, produce a all new visual (with my partners), move their website to a different web server, adapt it to mobile platforms, etc. Perhaps only ask some questions about their existing domain names or new domain names. </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr">I have listed some of the most frequently asked questions below to try to help you a little bit, but you can always use the contact form to inquire me about them.</p>\r\n<div class="grey" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>How long it will take to develop my web site/mobile site/mobile app?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">The time of a development project often depends of its complexity, but if you have a deadline in mind I’ll try to meet it for you. Regarding your interests, I’ve to warn you that the most common delay in a development project is waiting for client’s content (text/images).</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><strong>Once my website design is completed what aftersales service do you offer?</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr">We fully support any project we develop and are always available to solve any issues or enhancements. </p>\r\n<div class="grey" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Do I have to keep my project with you forever?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">No, once your project has been completed, it is yours and you can use as you want, since you respect the copyright. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><strong>If I contact you about a website, will it be "Search Engine" friendly?</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr">Depends. All websites are created having in mind the search engines, so they pass through a basic search engine optimization, but you can ask for a more complex SEO plan on your budget.</p>\r\n<div class="grey" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Can you provide all our web design, domain and hosting services?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Yes. Although I’m only the developer, I can manage all this requirements with my partners regarding to provide you a solution that satisfies you.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr"><strong>Do you use Flash animation in your websites?</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" dir="ltr">Usually don’t, as Flash carries on some issues, but I can provide it too.</p>\r\n<div class="grey" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Can I get personalized e-mail?</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Yes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 50px;" dir="ltr">If you would like to discuss a project with me please use the contact form (link), send me a direct e-mail to something@codingbooth.com, give me a call on <strong>+351 93 897 10 69</strong> or use one of the below platforms.</p>', '', 1, 8, '2013-07-23 14:28:16', 584, '', '2013-07-25 11:31:16', 584, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-07-23 14:28:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":null,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","s